{"tid":1349992,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[我無錯]我係警察","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:41:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T11:51:42.000Z","uid":213995,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8159838b62757f5d7582384c1ad953c001e4b4da","tid":1349992,"uid":213995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:41:39.000Z","msg":"其實諗諗下，敵人嘅敵人咪就係朋友囉。<br />\n<br />\n我地嘅敵人係示威者，示威者嘅敵人係黑社會，黑社會便是我朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我入左同幫黑社會大佬傾完，握完手交換埋ig咪出番黎散band囉。叫我班細嘅開埋路卑佢地走添啊。抄牌? 做乜鳩要抄自己人牌喎。<br />\n<br />\n我係警察嘅話死撚左佢算啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母死黑警</span></span>"},{"pid":"2b2a30c0bc1efd9b20e119c4e3d20d4f2e2e21f4","tid":1349992,"uid":213995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"黑社會吹雞 個個前一日都知啦，黑警你唔知? TVB提都冇提過知咩事啦"},{"pid":"d119bdd8e4ef19c75dff6fe059f1ff153757dc71","tid":1349992,"uid":213995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:45:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">見人惡你就驚 示威者冇還手能力就係咁打 警察喎</span></span>"},{"pid":"112a83fdc3f200c8e77927ebbfe7c1346a2c66df","tid":1349992,"uid":213995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"335d554dbfb57510654240dc9fa11c81e3a9ebba","tid":1349992,"uid":213995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:46:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">集氣咀咒黑警</span></span>"},{"pid":"2ef78a1e7375048b3db61b4c5ef85c3ca865a3f2","tid":1349992,"uid":213995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0bff9c9e3a4c0299d9e35d3506a631784116e254","tid":1349992,"uid":213995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:48:36.000Z","msg":"可能仲有有良知嘅警察嘅 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但唔該你企出黎反呢個&quot;司法機關&quot